  rss.nytimes.com/services/xml/rss/nyt/Politics.xml
  feeds.washingtonpost.com/rss/politics
  feeds.npr.org/1014/rss.xml
  moxie.foxnews.com/google-publisher/politics.xml
  feeds.nbcnews.com/nbcnews/public/news

Specialist publications — refresh every 30 minutes:
  cyberscoop.com/feed
  krebsonsecurity.com/feed
  statnews.com/feed
  who.int/rss-feeds/news-english.xml

Research institutions & think tanks — refresh once daily:
  rand.org/feed.xml
