For all RSS feeds:
- Apply keyword filtering to assign each item to one or more of these category
  IDs: geo, uspol, fin, tech, cyber, legal, safety, medical
- Run sentiment scoring (positive/negative/neutral) on each item
- Deduplicate by headline similarity within a 30-minute window
- Deduplication source priority: Reuters > AP > Bloomberg > BBC > Politico >
  all others

Keyword filter mapping:
  geo:     war, conflict, sanctions, NATO, China, Russia, Iran, missile,
           treaty, summit, invasion, ceasefire
  uspol:   Congress, Senate, House, Trump, Biden, election, midterm, SCOTUS,
