PHASED BUILD PLAN
================================================================================

PHASE 1 — Foundation
  - Set up GitHub repository and folder structure
  - Build Express server with single working endpoint
  - Connect Supabase database
  - Deploy to Railway
  - Confirm HTML can talk to backend
  Estimated time: 1-2 Claude Code sessions

PHASE 2 — Prediction Markets + VIX Live
  - Wire up Polymarket feed
  - Wire up Kalshi feed
  - Deduplication logic
  - 30-second polling confirmed working
  - VIX intraday feed via Yahoo Finance
  - FRED daily feed for all economic series
  - Live/Close indicator on VIX card
  Estimated time: 1 Claude Code session

PHASE 3 — News & Research Feeds
  - RSS breaking news feeds (13 sources)
  - RSS specialist feeds (4 sources)
  - RSS research/think tank feeds (9 sources)
  - Keyword filtering and sentiment scoring
  - Deduplication logic
  Estimated time: 1 Claude Code session

PHASE 4 — AI Consensus + GJOpen + Side-Panel & VIX Briefings
  - AI Platforms Consensus daily batch job (Claude simulating all models)
  - GET /api/consensus/:id endpoint
  - Update frontend to use cached consensus
  - POST /api/signal-briefing endpoint (6-hour cached briefings)
  - GET /api/vix-driver endpoint (30-min cached driver explainer)
  - Refactor all four direct api.anthropic.com fetches out of index.html
    so the browser never sees the Anthropic key
  - GJOpen daily scraper
  - Cross-reference layer (market vs. superforecaster comparison)
  Estimated time: 1-2 Claude Code sessions

PHASE 5 — Enterprise Pulse Survey (generation)
  - POST /api/pulse/generate-single endpoint
  - POST /api/pulse/generate-custom endpoint
  - Refactor index.html so both pulse flows call backend, not Anthropic
    directly
  - Verify frontend editable-questions UI (edit/delete/add) works against
    proxied responses
  Estimated time: 1 Claude Code session

PHASE 6 — Final Polish & Full Deployment
  - End-to-end testing of all feeds
  - Error handling and fallback states
  - Final front-end updates to consume all live endpoints
  - Full production deployment and monitoring setup
  Estimated time: 1 Claude Code session

